citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:20 am on
21-MAR-17.
Officials from the USDA and IDALS arrived at the facility at 11:20 am and spoke with a household member who
stated that the licensee was not available for the inspection.
